communi (1.1.0-5) unstable; urgency=low

  * Stability improvements
  * Handle mIRC background colors - thanks Mark Johnson!
  * Fix issue #5: The virtual keyboard does not appear on tapping
    the speech bubble on Harmattan PR1.2
  * Temporarily disabled automatic reconnection due to issue #6:
    Communi reconnects to the psyBNC server every 2 minutes

